OL,3,CEmployers expect private sector pay to
OL,4,Cincrease by 4% in 2024, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FEmployers believe pay will increase by
OL,8,F4% in 2024 in private firms, 1% lower
OL,9,Fthan previous years, research suggests.
OL,11,FIt is the first predicted fall since
OL,12,Fspring 2020, said the Chartered
OL,13,FInstitute of Personnel and Development
OL,14,F(CIPD).
OL,16,FPay expectations in the public sector
OL,17,Fhave fallen from 5% to 3%, said the
OL,18,Freport.
