OL,3,CEmployers expect private sector pay to
OL,4,Cincrease by 4% in 2024, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,F"Pay growth has helped individuals but
OL,8,Fit leaves employers with a higher wage
OL,9,Fbill to cover.
OL,11,F"To see a sustained return to growth,
OL,12,Fthere needs to be a real focus on
OL,13,Fboosting productivity by investing in
OL,14,Fworkplace skills and technology.
OL,16,F"It's also in employers' interest to
OL,17,Fcommunicate with employees their wider
OL,18,Fbenefits package and improve job
OL,19,Fquality to compensate if they are
OL,20,Fplanning to reduce base pay increases.
